{"tid":1419043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望連仔可以改善評分系統","createTime":"2019-08-05T23:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:17:46.000Z","uid":147010,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e8b1ec63f713a001025c40e2566e0e84f5bfc167","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:14:40.000Z","msg":"鑑於近日連登嘅正負評系統有不尋常嘅評分數量出現<br />\n尤其係一啲有導向分化嘅post<br />\n8月5日晚(8月6日凌晨)就有一個post可以短短個幾鐘有超過10,000正評<br />\n<br />\n根據各位資深巴絲嘅睇法，都認為數量多得唔尋常。即使計埋近日其他市民對連登嘅關注，於深夜時份短短個多小時就有如此大量評分，實屬不尋常<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">即使係真都好</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我建議連仔可以比用家選擇睇<span style=\"color: orange;\">非P牌嘅</span>評分，可以當作令一個參考指標<br />\n<br />\n大家都知道連登喺呢場運動上成為左好重要嘅平台(<span style=\"color: gold;\">多謝連仔，你比我地捐錢啦</span>，不論任何背景都可以用係網上討論區嘅威力。現時嘅P牌系統只可以方便識別帳號嘅開設時間，從而方便分別新舊用家嘅留言，<span style=\"color: orange;\">亦只有留言</span>。強烈建議連仔搵方法去分辨埋新舊用家嘅評分。<br />\n<br />\n有巴絲建議直接限制p牌用家權限，我唔肯定會唔會破壞登嘅風氣，因為由以前嘅高級會員頭像同埋而家嘅免廣告都唔涉及會員權限(以前好似會多啲PM？不過連仔冇PM系統)。慎防影響會員參與度，我再一次建議連仔改善評分系統，有舊會員同綜合會員嘅評分去做比較，睇下新舊會員之間嘅意向都好有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好話點解仲睇正負評，好簡單，呢個重來都係高登連登嘅特色，亦好明顯有一定參考性<br />\n冇理由眼見有漏動都唔去處理嫁嘛香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">懇求連仔更新會員評分系統以分辨新舊會員取態</span></span>"},{"pid":"57e849e1888ecb118b84ae707fb1bc78d612d3f2","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:15:16.000Z","msg":"自己10連推<br />\n無意分化，請顧全大局"},{"pid":"6fbd2366174974ec0756b650b410de6b1c115d22","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:16:18.000Z","msg":"1<br />\n杜絕評分系統被濫用"},{"pid":"b71e30db1481cdd8c98f6e963fe7735be80e2689","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:17:16.000Z","msg":"2<br />\n慎防懷疑惡意使用評分系統會員帶動風向"},{"pid":"af0e76516d8631a50cea468009ec5f97c603a38b","tid":1419043,"uid":109262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:17:55.000Z","msg":"幫手推<br />\n尋晚個風向好有問題"},{"pid":"94592471fc0469bd8c6679d5ab44201d6f122486","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:19:02.000Z","msg":"3<br />\n可借新/舊會員評分之取態促進交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42026292dcfff0c8882c7ff38a754a0752af240a","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:20:12.000Z","msg":"4<br />\n可以黎個公測，可能用半年後發現新會員減少就取消都冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78646fe1c58cd3058a09654a86f88a4d65ba5489","tid":1419043,"uid":4931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:20:45.000Z","msg":"同意，但第一批P牌就快 甩p"},{"pid":"3bcd8749d71c2f0134a5f8a7caea6a9cdd494c11","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:22:23.000Z","msg":"5<br />\n並非要分化會員，只係希望顯示更清晰數據以便會員分析開嘅post乎唔乎合會員預想"},{"pid":"7ff0cfde122558db15cb4c836fa47cea02eee5e7","tid":1419043,"uid":296715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:23:03.000Z","msg":"係喎,分開計好過直接停用,好橋"},{"pid":"27cc5cfb286cf61bb18bb3ebb0057d75c179fa6e","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:23:09.000Z","msg":"6<br />\n睇緊時事台，唔小心直接開左喺到，我認為適用於各台"},{"pid":"f1725682bde06e33817e06e36d194e70c3fd0f28","tid":1419043,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:23:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7a1cc7ea5d5f2c5c0b0d9e29ce9b412ba5a80c5","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:28:20.000Z","msg":"7<br />\n考完車牌個p就一年先甩，開個連登account就一個isp email就得，佢地冇咁快摸熟呢到嘅風氣嘅。我覺得要延長多半年，比佢地成為一堆新手社群，方便資深會員分辨呀嘛，廢事講完inside joke原來冇人明，好瘀嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cdeac6534fb75979ce6f29480f0899ef2be9f8f","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1725682bde06e33817e06e36d194e70c3fd0f28","tid":1419043,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:23:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:29:14.000Z","msg":"冇話block呀<br />\n我係提議有兩組或以上數據參考咋嘛"},{"pid":"f94b82ff966e44de2e9fcc5e464ee966c3a702b7","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:30:20.000Z","msg":"8<br />\n我只係提議提供2種以上評分數據比每一個全能嘅連登仔做研究"},{"pid":"9e6c6b3ad505cbfbd31169fdb65c7dff1810f669","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:31:29.000Z","msg":"9<br />\n如果怕有衝突，即使顯示設定係綜合數據都好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033f8b538684d7c557bfe8e864c5703e7659f0bb","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:31:48.000Z","msg":"10<br />\n請各位踴躍討論"},{"pid":"292364cd3f448194ae6972e9df52a6eaa95e04e5","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:33:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"acf84e80ca6db992419f49d3627c2a60a625cc7d","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:39:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed656c6ffb72e800b601ce4128fe4205583587bc","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:42:26.000Z","msg":"歡迎討論"},{"pid":"b4165ae869dc7c68469fa6e0362c6389a68ec3c1","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ce6204924d8a88398ff9d40b5ab2ad70e535e6","tid":1419043,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/no